    public static final String Rom_3_18 = "There is no fear of God before their eyes. ";
    public static final String Rom_3_19 = "Now we know that what things soever the law saith, it saith to them who are under the law: that every mouth may be stopped, and all the world may become guilty before God. ";
    public static final String Rom_3_20 = "Therefore by the deeds of the law there shall no flesh be justified in his sight: for by the law [is] the knowledge of sin. ";
    public static final String Rom_3_21 = "But now the righteousness of God without the law is manifested, being witnessed by the law and the prophets; ";
    public static final String Rom_3_22 = "Even the righteousness of God [which is] by faith of Jesus Christ unto all and upon all them that believe: for there is no difference: ";
    public static final String Rom_3_23 = "For all have sinned, and come short of the glory of God; ";
    public static final String Rom_3_24 = "Being justified freely by his grace through the redemption that is in Christ Jesus: ";
    public static final String Rom_3_25 = "Whom God hath set forth [to be] a propitiation through faith in his blood, to declare his righteousness for the remission of sins that are past, through the forbearance of God; ";
    public static final String Rom_3_26 = "To declare, [I say,] at this time his righteousness: that he might be just, and the justifier of him which believeth in Jesus. ";
    public static final String Rom_3_27 = "Where [is] boasting then? It is excluded. By what law? of works? Nay: but by the law of faith. ";
