    public static final String Rom_4_6 = "Even as David also describeth the blessedness of the man, unto whom God imputeth righteousness without works, ";
    public static final String Rom_4_7 = "[Saying,] Blessed [are] they whose iniquities are forgiven, and whose sins are covered. ";
