    public static final String Rom_5_1 = "Therefore being justified by faith, we have peace with God through our Lord Jesus Christ: ";
    public static final String Rom_5_2 = "By whom also we have access by faith into this grace wherein we stand, and rejoice in hope of the glory of God. ";
    public static final String Rom_5_3 = "And not only [so,] but we glory in tribulations also: knowing that tribulation worketh patience; ";
