    public static final String Rom_5_7 = "For scarcely for a righteous man will one die: yet peradventure for a good man some would even dare to die. ";
    public static final String Rom_5_8 = "But God commendeth his love toward us, in that, while we were yet sinners, Christ died for us. ";
    public static final String Rom_5_9 = "Much more then, being now justified by his blood, we shall be saved from wrath through him. ";
