    public static final String Rom_5_11 = "And not only [so,] but we also joy in God through our Lord Jesus Christ, by whom we have now received the atonement. ";
    public static final String Rom_5_12 = "Wherefore, as by one man sin entered into the world, and death by sin; and so death passed upon all men, for that all have sinned: ";
    public static final String Rom_5_13 = "(For until the law sin was in the world: but sin is not imputed when there is no law. ";
