    public static final String Rom_7_18 = "For I know that in me (that is, in my flesh,) dwelleth no good thing: for to will is present with me; but [how] to perform that which is good I find not. ";
    public static final String Rom_7_19 = "For the good that I would I do not: but the evil which I would not, that I do. ";
    public static final String Rom_7_20 = "Now if I do that I would not, it is no more I that do it, but sin that dwelleth in me. ";
