    public static final String Rom_11_4 = "But what saith the answer of God unto him? I have reserved to myself seven thousand men, who have not bowed the knee to [the image of] Baal. ";
    public static final String Rom_11_5 = "Even so then at this present time also there is a remnant according to the election of grace. ";
    public static final String Rom_11_6 = "And if by grace, then [is it] no more of works: otherwise grace is no more grace. But if [it be] of works, then is it no more grace: otherwise work is no more work. ";
