    public static final String Rom_11_10 = "Let their eyes be darkened, that they may not see, and bow down their back alway. ";
    public static final String Rom_11_11 = "I say then, Have they stumbled that they should fall? God forbid: but [rather] through their fall salvation [is come] unto the Gentiles, for to provoke them to jealousy. ";
    public static final String Rom_11_12 = "Now if the fall of them [be] the riches of the world, and the diminishing of them the riches of the Gentiles; how much more their fulness? ";
    public static final String Rom_11_13 = "For I speak to you Gentiles, inasmuch as I am the apostle of the Gentiles, I magnify mine office: ";
    public static final String Rom_11_14 = "If by any means I may provoke to emulation [them which are] my flesh, and might save some of them. ";
