    public static final String Rom_11_16 = "For if the firstfruit [be] holy, the lump [is] also [holy:] and if the root [be] holy, so [are] the branches. ";
    public static final String Rom_11_17 = "And if some of the branches be broken off, and thou, being a wild olive tree, wert graffed in among them, and with them partakest of the root and fatness of the olive tree; ";
    public static final String Rom_11_18 = "Boast not against the branches. But if thou boast, thou bearest not the root, but the root thee. ";
