    public static final String Rom_12_3 = "For I say, through the grace given unto me, to every man that is among you, not to think [of himself] more highly than he ought to think; but to think soberly, according as God hath dealt to every man the measure of faith. ";
    public static final String Rom_12_4 = "For as we have many members in one body, and all members have not the same office: ";
