    public static final String Rom_13_1 = "Let every soul be subject unto the higher powers. For there is no power but of God: the powers that be are ordained of God. ";
    public static final String Rom_13_2 = "Whosoever therefore resisteth the power, resisteth the ordinance of God: and they that resist shall receive to themselves damnation. ";
