    public static final String Rom_13_5 = "Wherefore [ye] must needs be subject, not only for wrath, but also for conscience sake. ";
    public static final String Rom_13_6 = "For for this cause pay ye tribute also: for they are God's ministers, attending continually upon this very thing. ";
    public static final String Rom_13_7 = "Render therefore to all their dues: tribute to whom tribute [is due;] custom to whom custom; fear to whom fear; honour to whom honour. ";
